Comment: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:01.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,淡々と続く Gray sky
Comment: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:07.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,刺激的な毎日 望むキミ
Comment: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:10.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,退屈しのぎ Loading game
Comment: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}孤独|ひとり{\k1}時間も Not so bad
Comment: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:17.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,止まってた針 動きだす
